div.p: healthcheck: pg_isready -U urluser -d urldb interval:5s retries:10
healthcheck: pg_isready -U analyticsuser -d analyticsdb interval:5s retries:10
healthcheck: pg_isready -U useruser -d userdb interval:5s retries:10
healthcheck: pg_isready -U notificationuser -d notificationdb interval:5s retries:10

div.h2: redis redis:7-alpine host:6379 container:6379 mode: ephemeral cache (--save "" --appendonly no)
rabbitmq rabbitmq:3.13-management-alpine host:5672 container:5672 (AMQP) host:15672 container:15672 (Mgmt UI)
div.p: healthcheck: rabbitmq-diagnostics ping interval:10s retries:10 start:20s

div.h2: url-service build: ./services/url-service host:8081 container:8080 ENV: DATABASE_URL REDIS_URL RABBITMQ_URL JWT_SECRET SHORT_URL_BASE IP_HASH_SALT
